<!-- How guidance sessions work -->
<div class="inner-block text">
  <h2 class="heading-medium">How guidance sessions work</h2>
</div>

<div class="grid-wrapper border-bottom">
  <div class="grid grid-1-2">
    <div class="inner-block">
      <p>Guidance sessions are free. You’ll talk to an experienced pension expert
        who will give you guidance about how to best use the money in your pension pot.</p>


      <p>You can book a session if:</p>

      <ul class="list-bullet">
        <li>you’re planning to take money from your pension pot in the next 6 months</li>
        <li>you have a pension based on how much has been paid into your pot</li>
        <li>you’re close to or over 55</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        <a rel="nofollow" href="/session-type" class="button button-get-started">Guidance sessions...</a>
      </p>

    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-1-2">
    <div class="grid grid-1-2">
      <div class="inner-block">
        <h3 class="heading-small">Book a phone session</h3>
        <p>Your session will be within 4 weeks of you making the booking.
          You’ll need to travel to a local guidance branch (up to 1 hour).</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-1-2">
      <div class="inner-block">
        <h3 class="heading-small">Book a face to face session</h3>
        <p>Your session will be within 5 days of you making the booking.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

